Step 1: Configure Tiled Properties
First, let's give these zones the data your game engine needs.

The Yellow Box (Speed Zone):

Select the yellow boxes.

Change their Class to Zone_SpeedLimit.

Add a Custom Property: Name: max_speed, Type: float (or int), Value: 30 (or whatever speed your game logic uses for slow driving).

The Grey Box (Zig-Zag / Crossing Zone):

Select the grey boxes.

Ensure their Class is Zig_Zag.

Add a Custom Property: Name: wait_time, Type: float, Value: 3.0 (This means a 3-second countdown).